Sample of complete Java back-end application using Spring 3.0 MVC as front end technology and 
Hibernate as backend ORM technology. For this application also uses Maven for build and dependency management and 
MySQL as database to persist the data.
 
The sample is based on excellent tutorial from "Spring 3.0 MVC Series": 
http://viralpatel.net/blogs/2010/11/spring3-mvc-hibernate-maven-tutorial-eclipse-example.html



